mme_unif <- function(n, a, b){
  x <- runif(n, a, b)
  t1 <- mean(x) - sqrt(3) * sd(x)
  t2 <- mean(x) + sqrt(3) * sd(x)
  c(t1, t2)
}

runif(n, t1, t2) unif(t1, t2) X n , n*1 vector X1, X2, , Xn R . mme_unif(n, a, b) . (a,b) X n mme theta1 theta2 mme return .
